, 
<materialsCitation pageId="57" pageNumber="115">
type locality not given. Restricted by W. Bergmans in 1991 to “ 
<collectingCountry box="[2050,2214,2417,2450]" name="Madagascar" pageId="57" pageNumber="115">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
.”
</materialsCitation>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="57" pageNumber="115" type="discussion">
Some authors consider 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Pollen in Schlegel &amp; Pollen" baseAuthorityYear="1866" box="[2336,2593,2458,2491]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Eidolon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="57" pageNumber="115" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="dupreanum">Eidolon dupreanum</taxonomicName>
a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Kerr" baseAuthorityYear="1792" box="[2225,2360,2505,2530]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Eidolon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="57" pageNumber="115" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="helvum">E. helvum</taxonomicName>
, but it is clearly distinct. Monotypic.
</subSubSection>
</paragraph>
